"Color Scheme

"Vscode Theme
"colorscheme codedark

"Gruvbox Theme
colorscheme gruvbox
set background=dark

"Dracula Theme
"colorscheme dracula

"Make Background Transparent after adding a ColorScheme.
autocmd VimEnter * hi Normal ctermbg=none

"Add Line Number
set number

"Nerd Tree Directory Configs

